# Class 39 Reading Notes

What are the benefits and downfalls of using the ‘getLastLocation()’ method to get your device’s location?
It uses significantly less battery than if you were to constantly update the location. 
The downfall is that it won't be that precise.

What about the ‘getCurrentLocation()’ method?
It gets a much more precise and up to date location. The downside is that it uses a significant amount of battery power.
